{
  "stem": "13911.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was a candle maker, and he was entitled to stay in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had the piece of paper that says [NON-ENGLISH], candle maker, and he's eligible to remain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So did his wife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But one morning she ventured out, and she did not have that piece of paper with her, and they ambushed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they did it like, ambush the ghetto, show your papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to have this piece of paper because, what do they care?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, they shoot you if you tell them you have it at home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe you're lying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, in the meantime, it didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Another one gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they shot her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was pleading, she has a piece of paper at home, but what did they care?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was shot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that man had that piece of paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, somebody I knew, knew him, and he said, I'm going to ask him, you have it?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It did not, really-- You see, the name was already Sarah Hirschhorn, which didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I didn't care what name I have, or what-- what year I was born.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But she was born in 1906.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, you know, when you're young, and such a discrepancy in ages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, when you're 15 and 18, you can get away with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But and especially, I was frail, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I-- I'm petite and I'm-- I was frail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was more, never looked my age.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Like, rather childish looking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "How can I be 1906?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So what I did is, I erased a zero and put a one on top of the zero.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Which, if you come and look at it closely, you can tell that it was tampered.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was afraid, already, to do more, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
